
get day of week by using date 
DateTime.Parse(“08/09/2022”).ToString(“dddd”) // MM/dd/yyyy


string to date formate 
 date = Datetime.ParseExact(input,“MM/dd/yyyy”,System.Globalization.CultureInfo.InvariantCulture)
 
 
 
